Qualys SSL Labs 的 SSL Server Test 工具，可以帮你查出 HTTPS 很多配置上的问题:
https://www.ssllabs.com/ssltest/analyze.html

如:
https://www.ssllabs.com/ssltest/analyze.html?d=www.stackoverflowchina.com
https://www.ssllabs.com/ssltest/analyze.html?d=imququ.com

https://blog.myssl.com/ocsp-must-staple/
OCSP Must Staple	No
浏览器是否必须检测OCSP响应
